  qemu-kvm-0.11.1.ebuild:
  Comment out pie and stack-protector filtering, remove with next version,
  if there are no complains

  15 Dec 2009; Doug Goldstein <cardoe@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  change to qemu herd

